title: Blacklist
description: The Blacklist is a mid-wide, true-twin shape with a medium to soft flex. Powerful versatility in a mid-wide rocker package; the Blacklist is ideal for a park driven approach to any mountain or man-made terrain. Bank on big return and the durability and control needed for technical tricks, big landings, and risky ventures…
